Mother, wife and actress, Funke Akindele has said that her friends are not allowed to call her hubby except on his birthday. She made this view known during her interview/discussion on TVC programme, “Your View” “Unless it’s his birthday, it’s wrong for my best friend to call my husband “, she said…. Watch video: Unless it’s his birthday, it’s wrong for my best friend to call my husband – Funke Akindele🎥: @TVCconnect pic.twitter.com/ww2A9Pgkl0